Up in space a asteroid belt causes a pod to leave orbit and hit earth 
almost a shade of 3 miles from where the big battle is taking place. 
In a swamp the pod scans a frog and with the maximal signature He 
arises as Springer the tree frog. springer instantly realizes he can 
change colors to hide in the wild with this he hops on a lilly pad 
seeing gunfire from the base and seeing is is just getting used to 
being a Maximal than Autobot he waits until the battle calms down.
